{"lemma":"عامَّة","slug":"عامَّة","root":"ع.م.م","root_slug":"ع-م-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-م-م","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عامّ","root":"عوم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":9},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30607","n31089"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"year","examples":[{"text":"وَلَقَدْ أَرْسَلْنَا نُوحًا إِلَى قَوْمِهِ فَلَبِثَ فِيهِمْ أَلْفَ سَنَةٍ إِلَّا خَمْسِينَ عَامًا فَأَخَذَهُمُ ٱلطُّوفَانُ وَهُمْ ظَالِمُونَ فَأَنْجَيْنَاهُ وَأَصْحَابَ ٱلسَّفِينَةِ وَجَعَلْنَاهَا آيَةً لِلْعَالَمِينَ","english":"And We certainly sent Noah to his people, and he remained among them nine hundred and fifty years, and the flood seized them while they were wrongdoers. But We saved him and the companions of the ship, and We made it a sign for the worlds."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a period of twelve lunar months; lunar year"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"public"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"prevalent, universal"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"general","examples":[{"text":"بلغت نسبة التصويت العامة في إسرائيل حتى الساعة الثامنة 62% وهي اقل 2.6% عن عام 2015.","english":"Voter turnout for the general population of Israel as of 8:00 reached 62%, which is 2.6% less than in the year 2015."}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"common, ordinary"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to float"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to swim"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Since this word competes with سَنَة (sana), عَام (ʕām) is suggested to be loaned from Old South Arabian 𐩲𐩣 (ʿm /⁠*ʿām⁠/, “year”). Compare Ge'ez ዓም (ʿam, “year”).\n\nDerived from the active participle of عَمَّ (ʕamma, “to be general, to be common, to prevail”) (cognate to Hebrew עַם (am, “nation”) and עֲמָמִי ('amamí, “public”)). Contamination from Parthian 𐫍𐫀𐫖 (hʾm /⁠hām-⁠/, “same”) or its Middle Iranian analogues such as engendering Old Armenian համ- (ham-, “same, homo-; whole, pan-”) is considered."},"ipa":["/ʕaːm/","/ʕaːmm/","/ʕaː.ma/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30607","headword_ar":"عَامِهٌ","root":"Emh","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamihN","text_ar":"عَمِهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n31089","headword_ar":"عَامَةٌ","root":"Ewm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of float, such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tawof","text_ar":"طَوْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which one embarks on the water;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) accord. to AA,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miEobar","text_ar":"مِعْبَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is upon rivers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA:) in the M, said to be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that is made of the branches of trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, upon which one crosses a river, and which tosses about upon the water"},{"kind":"text","text":"the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmaAtN","text_ar":"عَامَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ewm","text_ar":"عوم"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuwmN","text_ar":"عُومٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuwqN","text_ar":"نُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] and [coll. gen. n.] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmN","text_ar":"عَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAm~apN","text_ar":"عَامَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EimaAmapN","text_ar":"عِمَامَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"head of a ruler,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a rider upon a camel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"haAmapu raAkibK","text_ar":"هَامَةُ رَاكِبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when it appears to thee in the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desert,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plain, called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHoraA='","text_ar":"صَحْرَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K. TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as he is journeying:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or it is not"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2203},{"kind":"text","text":"thus called unless"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having upon it a turban."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A turn,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twist, of a turban."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) [See 2, second sentence.] ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A quantity"},{"kind":"text","text":"of reaped corn"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"placed, in handfuls:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. [or rather coll. gen. n.] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmN","text_ar":"عَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Az","TA"]}]}}